== Tout.IO / Timed Sales

Timed Sales is a Shopify App to control store sales.

== Roadmap pre-0.1

  |-- Home/Dashboard
      |-- Activity Log
      |   |-- Name
      |   `-- Description
      `-- Sales
          `-- Create
              |-- Name
              |-- Descrption
              |-- Product
              `-- Sale Price

